data.description: Check out this beautiful 4 bed, 2 1/2 bath home on a sprawling .61 acre lot in the desirable Hunters Point neighborhood in Spartanburg, SC! Brimming with curb appeal and charm, this well maintained home has so much to offer! Upon entry into the home you are greeted by the spacious living room, with a lovely fire place nestled into the corner. You’ll notice beautiful hardwood floors from the foyer through the arched doorway into the kitchen and dining area! The chef of your family will love this huge eat in kitchen which boasts white cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, island with bar seating and generous dining area. The large main floor master bedroom features trey ceiling, walk-in closet and en-suite bath with a jetted tub and separate shower! Upstairs is where you'll discover 3 additional spacious bedrooms, each with ample closet space and another full bathroom. Step out back onto a large deck overlooking your perfectly manicured level fenced backyard! An added bonus is the storage shed/workshop with electric. With all these great features and a fantastic location less than 3 miles to I-85 and convenient to both Spartanburg and Greenville, this fantastic home is a gem! Don’t delay to schedule your private showing!
